
.. py:class:: pystk2.GraphicsConfig

   SuperTuxKart graphics configuration.


   .. py:method:: hd () -> pystk2.GraphicsConfig
      :staticmethod:

      High-definitaiton graphics settings


   .. py:method:: ld () -> pystk2.GraphicsConfig
      :staticmethod:

      Low-definition graphics settings


   .. py:method:: none () -> pystk2.GraphicsConfig
      :staticmethod:

      Disable graphics and rendering


   .. py:method:: sd () -> pystk2.GraphicsConfig
      :staticmethod:

      Standard-definition graphics settings


   .. py:property:: animated_characters () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Animate characters


   .. py:property:: bloom () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable the bloom effect


   .. py:property:: degraded_IBL () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Disable specular IBL


   .. py:property:: display_adapter () -> int
      :annotation: property

      GPU to use (Linux only)


   .. py:property:: dof () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Depth of field effect


   .. py:property:: dynamic_lights () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable dynamic lighting


   .. py:property:: glow () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable glow around pickup objects


   .. py:property:: high_definition_textures () -> int
      :annotation: property

      Enable high definition textures 0 / 2


   .. py:property:: light_shaft () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable light shafts


   .. py:property:: mlaa () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable anti-aliasing


   .. py:property:: motionblur () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable motion blur


   .. py:property:: particles_effects () -> int
      :annotation: property

      Particle effect 0 (none) to 2 (full)


   .. py:property:: render () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Is rendering enabled?


   .. py:property:: screen_height () -> int
      :annotation: property

      Height of the rendering surface


   .. py:property:: screen_width () -> int
      :annotation: property

      Width of the rendering surface


   .. py:property:: ssao () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Enable screen space ambient occlusion


   .. py:property:: texture_compression () -> bool
      :annotation: property

      Use texture compression


.. py:function:: pystk2.init (config: pystk2.GraphicsConfig) -> None

   Initialize Python SuperTuxKart - this will download the game assets if not already done. Only call this function once per process. Calling it twice will cause a crash.


.. py:function:: pystk2.clean () -> None

   Free Python SuperTuxKart, call this once at exit (optional). Will be called atexit otherwise.

